**Purpose:** A visual complement to the prose in `1-cynefin-framing.md` → `7-adr/`. Each diagram closes a specific prose gap; none duplicates the written artifacts.

**Coverage:** {{TOTAL_COUNT}} diagrams shipped by `/ddd:diagrams`. The skill chose this set based on detected signals in the project (see Phase 2 recommendation transcript in the run log). Skipped IDs and reasons are recorded in the [diagram catalog](../../../kb/patterns/ddd-diagram-catalog.md).

